# Project Memory

## Core

- Themes: **Midnight Emerald** (default) or Classic. User picks in Settings; stored as `theme` in `chrome.storage.local`.
- Midnight Emerald: oklch palette, glassmorphism, teal glow — see `midnight-emerald-theme.md` / `theme.css`.
- Plus Jakarta Sans display, Amiri for Arabic. RTL support for Arabic text.
- Prayer times app: bilingual EN/AR, live countdown, AlAdhan API, Riyadh default.

